          <b><span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">ἐπι - πταίρω</span></b> , aor. <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">ἐπέπταρε</span>: <span class="alpheios-lex-gloss">sneeze at;</span>
          <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">τινὶ ἐπέεσσιν</span> (at one's words, a lucky
